    "body": "Interestingly \n\n``` c\n#include<sys/stat.h>\n\nint main(){\n    struct stat sb;\n    stat(\"tc\", &sb);\n    printf(\"%d %d\\n\", S_ISLNK(sb.st_mode), (sb.st_mode & S_IFMT) == S_IFLNK);\n    return 0;\n}\n```\n\nalso prints a `0 0`\u2026 (where tc is obviously a symlink)\n",
