    "updated_at": "2015-10-25T16:01:31Z",
    "body": "The problem here is that `stat`/`metadata` follows symbolic links. You must use [`symlink_metadata`](http://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/std/fs/fn.symlink_metadata.html) to retrieve information about file without following symbolic links.\n\nEDIT: I\u2019d close this as WONTFIX since documentation for `metadata` clearly states this behaviour too.\n",
